      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MALICIOUS (4) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, holding on for a minor placing when third and beaten 1.5 lengths at The Gardens over 600m in 34.84. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Can find winning form. OLIVER GO (8) goes very well this course and distance starting seven times for three wins and two minors. Hit the frame latest (34.57) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Can feature in the finish. ROMA KEEPING (1) turned in a better effort at Q Lakeside last start, finishing second behind Surrealist (30.80) in a Grade 4/5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in this for a long way. ZEPHYR (2) is one of the chances after a minor prize in quick time last start.",
